Use Expo EAS Build:

npx expo install eas-cli
npx eas build:configure
npx eas build --platform android


You’ll get a download link to share like:

https://expo.dev/artifacts/....

in you account from here > https://expo.dev/accounts/accountName/projects/Auth-app/builds


People can install the APK directly.

APK

Run this command in your project folder:

npx eas build --platform android --profile preview

Install on Android devices

On the phone, go to Settings → Security → Enable “Install unknown apps” (if not from Play Store)

Open the link or APK file in the browser

Tap Install


